name: New Beginnings?
description:
Parents will leave home for a 5 day holiday.

Wow! finally here is some real free time for me.

But somehow they decided to come back early, wait, I haven't prepared yet!

Note: There is sound in this game!

Controls

A & D - Move

K / Space - Jump

(hold)J - Pick up

Credits
